				>
					<Icon name="mdi:codepen" class="mr-2 h-7 w-7" />CodePen Snippets
				</a>
			</li>
			<li class="m-0">
				<details class="my-[0.25rem]">
					<summary class="py-4 text-center text-lg font-bold"
						>Browse My Personal Social Media</summary
					>
					<p class="mx-6 text-center">
						I have a variety of hobbies and interests that I stay updated on using my personal
